messages:
Name: Fehmi Mert Günok
Nationality: Turkey
Date of Birth: March 1, 1989
Position: Goalkeeper
Current club: İstanbul Başakşehir
Süper Lig clubs played for: Fenerbahçe, Bursaspor, İstanbul Başakşehir

İstanbul Başakşehir's Fehmi Mert Günok has taken part in a strong number of their Süper Lig games in 2020/2021, making 21 appearances overall and playing 1,890 minutes. He has started in all 21 of these appearances across their 40 fixtures.

The last league appearance that Günok made came on May 15 for İstanbul Başakşehir in a 2-0 win against Rizespor; a match that he played 90 minutes in and kept a clean sheet. He has kept six Süper Lig clean sheets this term.
Günok played 33 Süper Lig games last season for İstanbul Başakşehir, keeping a total of 10 clean sheets, while also providing one assist.
Günok moved to İstanbul Başakşehir in August 2017 from Bursaspor, for whom he made 20 league appearances in total.
